{title: Spirits Of St. Louis}
{artist: Johnny Paycheck}
{composer: Written by Roger Bowling and Robert Jones}

[C]Well the barrooms close at two A.M.  [F]in St. Louis
[G7]And I'm always the last one out the [C]door
